{"tid":1912461,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［重要］燒生話黃標情況仍然嚴重，會轉戰patron，請繼續youtube聯署","createTime":"2020-03-06T05:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T13:04:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79f2a079ef1fdaa463bc0919a44561eccb8ee414","tid":1912461,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T05:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SECeIovpvGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSECeIovpvGQ&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=4f2454ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SECeIovpvGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n最後5分鐘<br />\n<br />\n所以請繼續聯署<br />\n中招既KOL唔該cap 低哂所有證據<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位朋友, 幫手發這個聯署出去, 幫手找人簽<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=53dc9fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-youtube-explain-why-youtubers-are-censored-or-no-ads-yellow-icons-coronavirus-topic</a><br />\n這個聯署是請求白宮要求youtube解釋為什麼限制談及武漢肺炎的題目? 為什麼限制言論自由? 希望大家幫手發出去, 因為被黃標了, 會影響收入, 是中共打壓言論自由的手段之一, 不可以就這樣被人打壓<br />\n<br />\nGoogle is censoring legitimate YouTube videos about the new coronavirus in China<br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/nQWTBG8Mcj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FnQWTBG8Mcj&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=b7523de8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/nQWTBG8Mcj</a><br />\n另外這個國際聯署反對Youtube限制言論自由<br />\n麻煩都簽埋<br />\n<br />\n(聯署)要求白宮問Youtube點解限制言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1906939\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1906939</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c66121f498f913b60b